This is NYC and this place is within Wall Street. The expectations are high and this place answers the call. It’s really large, and has the largest selection of food offerings in the area. It was late afternoon when I stopped by for a latte but I’m sure during lunch hours that this place is rocking. There’s plenty of dining, with a upstairs dining area that’s reached by a surprisingly out of place staircase. It’s a nice staircase that would seem to have come from a Victorian styled house. Very awesome to take photos on. It’s kind of pricey but that’s solely based on the money making area. I didn’t have time to eat but I could have sat down with some vegetarian food and even had a beer. Nice place. #nyc #wallstreet #nycfood #sankofatafari #kingofcoffeenyc #nyc
